{"tid":406550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好奇一問 賭錢依個方法可唔可行","createTime":"2017-09-19T17:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T07:48:40.000Z","uid":57531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2908798d536eea453e2592af7a8459a94d404cc1","tid":406550,"uid":57531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"假設贏就double既情況下<br />\n<br />\nStep1:如果我冇錢我借人1蚊去賭<br />\ncase1:變2蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n贏輸我都借人2蚊再賭<br />\ncase1:變4蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁終有一日我會贏既話，咪會賺錢？（假如而家停就4-2-1=賺1蚊）<br />\n<br />\n利申：sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"94148dca61ed42109845510ca7ad0a3cdd0ac6c4","tid":406550,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"乜宜家啲大學生咁戇鳩<br />\n收手啦。。。"},{"pid":"f0c945a0f3f29f44dab5f99ab6893aa8006cc192","tid":406550,"uid":8178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設贏就double既情況下<br />\n<br />\nStep1:如果我冇錢我借人1蚊去賭<br />\ncase1:變2蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n贏輸我都借人2蚊再賭<br />\ncase1:變4蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁終有一日我會贏既話，咪會賺錢？（假如而家停就4-2-1=賺1蚊）<br />\n<br />\n利申：sorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n你個賭本要幾何級數咁上<br />\n有冇人借比你先"},{"pid":"5cac4a4f09c5b96aad81c0d5900cc5ab036688f2","tid":406550,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"贏縮輸谷借錢版"},{"pid":"79bde9bb64de56e16c8b35050dd59e4542adaffb","tid":406550,"uid":76428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"咪即係濕鳩倫敦金囉<br />\n借既人冇得益 即係你要呃先借到"},{"pid":"c8505072b74a9b319a00f3e7da9ebf5b55d98e8c","tid":406550,"uid":110761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"呢個叫賭纜<br />\n通常用係賭場買大細度<br />\n的確係必贏<br />\n但有兩個前提<br />\n無限本同受注金額無上限<br />\n呢兩樣根本無可能滿足到<br />\n而且係用好多好多去贏一注嘅錢<br />\n而一斷纜就乜都無"},{"pid":"d3ddf319e7f214f0d64a0b709fa8ac9be0a1b40e","tid":406550,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"本多終勝"},{"pid":"5d6257c83da792dc0491451cfe29fcd2688d2c64","tid":406550,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T21:08:09.000Z","msg":"中國13億人口，你每個都乞一蚊，你都有13億啦"},{"pid":"a639b25f93a5b73ed47be9ad64ad4f49cf0eea44","tid":406550,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T21:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國13億人口，你每個都乞一蚊，你都有13億啦</blockquote><br />\n中學曾經諗過,係班到求奇搵廿個人.每人借1蚊,我嗰日食飯就唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682cf4d8661f12dd923771b730ae841781b6684f","tid":406550,"uid":13901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T21:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國13億人口，你每個都乞一蚊，你都有13億啦</blockquote><br />\n中學曾經諗過,係班到求奇搵廿個人.每人借1蚊,我嗰日食飯就唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實work<br />\n你見成日有人開post<br />\n話係街到有人問佢借錢<br />\n就知好大機會係條友周圍問人借或者直接講係乞錢<br />\n夠厚面皮可以生活到一段日子"},{"pid":"64cdbf3762e53ac46c66b5ab527661e249d47011","tid":406550,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設贏就double既情況下<br />\n<br />\nStep1:如果我冇錢我借人1蚊去賭<br />\ncase1:變2蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n贏輸我都借人2蚊再賭<br />\ncase1:變4蚊<br />\ncase2:咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">終有一日我會贏</span>既話，咪會賺錢？（假如而家停就4-2-1=賺1蚊）<br />\n<br />\n利申：sorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前提係你要贏囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十賭九輸喎<br />\n仲要問人借錢 輸咗咪爭落周身債...<br />\n如果係咁易贏錢既話 馬會會年年賺咁多錢咩 澳門會有咁多賭場咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}